name: Diamond Animals Karakurt
description:
Diamond Animals Karakurt - 1 of 10 art from the "Diamond Animals" collection.

Karakurt is a species of black widow spider. The ancient Indian tradition calls the creator of all things Brahma - a spider that weaves the world from a web-matter.
This diamond karakurt can create the most incredible worlds.
